{"tid":497682,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖東近依一年多左班人!","createTime":"2017-12-13T04:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T07:36:17.000Z","uid":58675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"759c30c274e2dd5944c8572dd0595adb8b864594","tid":497682,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T04:40:59.000Z","msg":"我想講好耐了~無論返工放工朝早夜晚無時無刻有班大陸閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一群群拖撚住個喼周圍走，一車車旅遊巴送哂入某一棟商業大廈度! 男既著住好撚柒既西裝(浸味柒到由腳指尾柒到上頭殼頂) 女既就鬼五馬六著住土味甚濃既OL suit...亂鳩咁配搭...又肉C閃C加boot型高跟鞋...個撚個日里萬機咁以為著左老西或suit就扮哂中環專業人士咁係尖東遊走...早餐Lunch已經進佔哂所有食市...(美心/太興輪為重災區)。<br />\n有無巴絲知佢地做咩!? 又係傳銷!?定係買啲濕鳩Products之後上返鬼國轉售!?<br />\n家下尖東除左自由行就係多左班咁既人!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3c3a653e3e2b0a90659c282d78a1a77b4c9afd","tid":497682,"uid":56432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"亞皆老街近窩打老道都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲大陸著哂啲東門style 縮水西裝立到個頭又七又笠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d53c8c2ffb078e18648eea6e96268114f16666e","tid":497682,"uid":58675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T05:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/133749_687946e85a69cbb148e3ba98f8a9fd5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F133749_687946e85a69cbb148e3ba98f8a9fd5e.jpg&h=d67e0210&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/133754_b326694ba5d50ac67b8ae440f0797ac6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F133754_b326694ba5d50ac67b8ae440f0797ac6.jpg&h=d0108a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係就被依班鴨仔團佔領<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee72ead4221b563e1383d86712d739d06154889","tid":497682,"uid":58675,"